<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<section xml:id="section-3" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Span of a set of vectors</title>
  <p>
    In this section, we will discuss the span of a set of vectors. 
  </p>
   <definition xml:id="def-linear-transformation">
      <statement>
        <p>A transformation <m>T:R^n\rightarrow R^m</m> is a 
          linear transformation if it satisfies the following two 
          properties for all <m>\vec{x},\vec{y}\in\R^n</m> and all 
          scalars <m>a\in R</m>.
        </p>
      </statement>
    </definition>
  </section>